{
  "stem": "26728.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had-- you were dragged all over the neighborhood because you couldn't-- the dogs were very powerful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Father Stoner was a very strict and businesslike man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's-- I don't recall having any real friendly, warm feelings toward him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He insisted on his altar boys being-- learning precisely the way he wanted them to say mass, the way his-- their mannerisms and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I don't have fond recollections of that part of my religious training.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I learned Latin through him-- some Latin, of course-- since that's how they said mass in those days.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I began, when I was in my early teens, to question some, some of the Catholic dogma, and I kind of just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Over my mother's objections, I kind of just dropped out of the Church for several years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was-- I was interested in sports, mostly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very athletic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother was, too, although he was much smaller than me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a terrific swimmer, and I was, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the benefits of living in Tucson, which was very hot, was that we, in the summertime, spent most of the time in the swimming pools.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had numerous public pools that-- very inexpensive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My brother became a real champion diver and a very fast swimmer. 18 months younger than me, but-- and I was much bigger and stronger than him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he could swim, and he was fearless diving off of 60-foot platforms into the water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I would jump.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I jumped many times from that platform before I had the courage to dive off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But Ben, my Benny-- I called him Benny-- he just wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he was really-- he was not big enough to play football.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
